===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|absteiner}}, from {{m|enm|absteinen||to abstain}}. More at {{l|en|abstain}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/æbˈsteɪ.nɚ/}}
